headline.print_headline: Biden, African Leaders Talk Economy, Security
headline.main: Biden, African Leaders Talk Economy, Security

lead_paragraph: Vice President Joe Biden has been talking with several African leaders on topics ranging from economic cooperation to security during the summit meeting aimed at strengthening U.S. ties with Africa.
